---
---

<section id="about" class="py-20 px-6 bg-[#EEF7F4]">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">

      <!-- Left Column — Image -->
      <div class="aspect-[3/4] overflow-hidden rounded-3xl shadow-lg">
        <img
          src="/images/IMG_5113.jpg"
          alt="Dr. Shilpa Pandya, Paediatrician at Paediatric Wellness, Hoodi Bengaluru"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover object-top"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column — Content -->
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-5 text-center lg:text-left items-center lg:items-start">
        <!-- Eyebrow -->
        <p class="text-[#E8856A] text-sm font-medium italic tracking-wide">
          About the Doctor
        </p>

        <!-- Name -->
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-[#2E2B3D] leading-tight" style="font-family: 'Nunito', sans-serif;">
          Dr. Shilpa Pandya
        </h2>

        <!-- Subtitle -->
        <p class="text-[#E8856A] font-semibold">
          Paediatrician &amp; Consultant
        </p>

        <!-- Bio -->
        <p class="text-[#706C82] leading-relaxed">
          Dr. Shilpa Pandya is a dedicated paediatrician with over 15 years of experience caring for children from infancy through adolescence. She completed her MD in Paediatrics from Gandhi Medical College, Bhopal, and has served families at Hiranandani Hospital, bringing warmth and expertise to every consultation.
        </p>
        <p class="text-[#706C82] leading-relaxed">
          She pursued advanced training under MUHS Nashik and completed her internship at the prestigious JJ &amp; Grant Medical Colleges. Her commitment to lifelong learning keeps her at the forefront of evidence-based paediatric practice.
        </p>

        <!-- Credential Badges -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-2 justify-center lg:justify-start">
          <span class="bg-white rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium shadow-sm border border-gray-100 text-[#2E2B3D]">
            MD Paediatrics · Gandhi Medical College, Bhopal
          </span>
          <span class="bg-white rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium shadow-sm border border-gray-100 text-[#2E2B3D]">
            Post Graduate Paediatric Nutrition · Boston University
          </span>
          <span class="bg-white rounded-full px-4 py-2 text-sm font-medium shadow-sm border border-gray-100 text-[#2E2B3D]">
            Lifetime Member · Indian Academy of Paediatrics (IAP)
          </span>
        </div>

        <!-- Work Experience -->
        <div class="mt-4">
          <p class="text-[#706C82] text-sm font-medium mb-3">Work experience with</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-6 justify-center lg:justify-start">
            <img src="/images/apolloLogo.webp" alt="Apollo Hospitals" class="h-10 object-contain" loading="lazy" />
            <img src="/images/Jeevika-2-1.png.bv_resized_mobile.png.bv.webp" alt="Jeevika Hospital" class="h-10 object-contain" loading="lazy" />
            <img src="/images/unnamed.png" alt="Hiranandani Hospital" class="h-10 object-contain" loading="lazy" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>
